    >>> x1 = DecisionVariable.integer(1)
    >>> x2 = DecisionVariable.integer(2)
    >>> g = 2*x1 + 3*x2 + 1

    Compare two linear functions with tolerance:

    >>> f.almost_equal(g, atol=1e-12)
